{"comments":"Fluid Particle — SPH (Smoothed Particle Hydrodynamics) simulation.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nBased on the SIGGRAPH Asia 2022 paper \"Neighborhood Search for SPH\"\nand classic SPH fluid dynamics. Particles carry mass, position,\nvelocity, and material properties.\n\n## SPH Fundamentals\n\nEach particle represents a sample of the fluid. Properties are\nsmoothed using kernel functions:\n\n  A(r) = Σ_j m_j * (A_j / ρ_j) * W(r - r_j, h)\n\nWhere:\n- m_j = particle mass\n- ρ_j = particle density\n- W = smoothing kernel\n- h = smoothing radius\n\n## Kernel Functions\n\n- **Poly6**: General interpolation\n- **Spiky**: Pressure forces (avoids particle clumping)\n- **Viscosity**: Viscous forces\n\n## Dependencies\n- Prelude\n- Data.Array\n- Data.Maybe\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"A single SPH particle.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["id",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["x",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["y",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["vx",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["vy",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["mass",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["density",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["pressure",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["viscosity",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"RE